SLOPPY JOE MAC N CHEESE

What is SLOPPY JOE?

SLOPPY JOE is a sandwich consisting of ground beef, onion, tomato sauce, worcestershire sauce, brown sugar and other seasonings, served on a Hamburger bun. This dish originated in US during the early 20th century.

SLOPPY JOE MAC N CHEESE takes the flavors of Sloppy Joe and put them in a comfort pasta.
